body:
> Should we report all difference compared to latest Vim version

Absolutely not. 

I am not interested in spending lots of time on pedantic correctness in this area. If we are missing major notes, we can note them. But I don't want to spend time on nitpicking, in this context.

"Batch" updates that are not too verbose are welcome, but I want to avoid lots of tiny corrections in dozens of PRs.
